statshed-cli (1.0.2) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial Go release: from-scratch port of the Python statshed-cli with the
    same commands, flags, configuration, and exit codes, shipped as a single
    dependency-free binary.
  * Includes the submit, stream, wrap, health, groups, jobs, config,
    group-config, and completion commands.

